00:23:09.968 --> 00:23:11.169
(intense orchestra music)

00:23:11.203 --> 00:23:13.271
[Narrator] With Tai and
the others in danger,

00:23:13.305 --> 00:23:15.807
Sora's Digivice lights up.

00:23:15.841 --> 00:23:17.008
[Tai Voiceover] Next time on

00:23:17.042 --> 00:23:20.345
"Digimon Adventure
2020: Birdramon Soars!"

00:23:20.378 --> 00:23:23.014
[Narrator] The adventure
continues in a new world.

